### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health


### Get all assets from MongoDB
GET http://localhost:8080/api/assets


### Get one asset
# Replace the ID below with an actual ID returned by GET /api/assets
GET http://localhost:8080/api/assets/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ID


### Get missing asset
GET http://localhost:8080/api/assets/000000000000000000000000

### Filter assets by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/assets?status=AVAILABLE

#### Filter assets by category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/assets?category=Phone

### Filter assets by location
GET http://localhost:8080/api/assets?location=HQ%20Level%67

### Get paged assets
GET http://localhost:8080/api/assets/paged?page=0&size=5

### Get paged assets sorted by name in descending order
GET http://localhost:8080/api/assets/paged?page=0&size=5&sortBy=name&direction=desc

### Get paged assets sorted by category in ascending order
GET http://localhost:8080/api/assets/paged?page=0&size=5&sortBy=category&direction=asc


### Create a valid asset
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assetTag": "TAB-2026-001",
  "name": "Samsung Galaxy Tab",
  "category": "Tablet",
  "serialNumber": "SN-TAB-001",
  "location": "HQ Level 4"
}


### Create an invalid asset
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assetTag": "",
  "name": "",
  "category": "",
  "serialNumber": "",
  "location": ""
}
